**Editor-in-Chief**
The helm is steered by **[Marc Mézard](/Marc_M%C3%A9zard)**, a figure associated with **[CNRS](/CNRS)**, **[University of Paris-Sud](/University_of_Paris-Sud)**, and **[École Normale Supérieure](/%C3%89cole_Normale_Sup%C3%A9rieure)**. A rather formidable list of affiliations, suggesting a mind that is both deeply immersed in the field and well-connected within the academic hierarchy. He’s the one ultimately responsible for the journal’s direction and quality.

